## dma-names

A list of strings providing names for the corresponding entries in the `dmas` property.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/qcom/sm8550.dtsi */
uart7: serial@880000 {
    dmas = <&gpi_dma1 0 7 QCOM_GPI_UART>,
           <&gpi_dma1 1 7 QCOM_GPI_UART>;
    dma-names = "tx", "rx";
};
```
